# Solutions Knowledge Base

This directory contains structured solution documents created by `/compound`.

Each solution captures:
- Problem description and symptoms
- Failed approaches and why they didn't work
- Root cause analysis
- Working solution with explanation
- Prevention guidance

## Directory Structure

```
docs/solutions/
├── build-errors/
├── test-failures/
├── runtime-errors/
├── performance/
├── config-errors/
├── dependencies/
├── integrations/
├── logic-errors/
├── design-flaws/
├── infrastructure/
└── security/
```

## Usage

### Search for relevant solutions:
```bash
grep -riwl "keyword" docs/solutions/
```

### Find by severity:
```bash
grep -rl "severity: high" docs/solutions/
```

### Add a new solution:
```
/compound
```
